messages.title: The Truth About UKIP
messages.content:
Keep the NHS free at point of delivery
An Australian-style, points based, fairer Immigration system
Scrap HS2 - Save at least £80 billion!
No to Over-development, Community Led Planning and not opportunist developers

keyPolicies.policyDescription: Keep the NHS free at point of delivery. UKIP will ensure £3 billion extra to the NHS to keep it free.
An Australian-style, points based, fairer Immigration system. UKIP opposes unlimited immigration and supports controlled immigration.
Scrap HS2 - Save at least £80 billion. Funds should be spent on infrastructure such as roads, footpaths, schools and hospitals.
No to Over-development, Community Led Planning and not opportunist developers. Housing priority for local people.
No tax on the minimum wage. Opposes the 'bedroom tax' and the 'mansion tax'.
Opposes £12 billion a year in foreign aid.
